    <title type="html"><![CDATA[安装 Redis:一步至简]]></title>
    <link href="http://redispw.github.io/blog/2013/07/02/setup-redis/"/>
    <updated>2013-07-02T00:03:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://redispw.github.io/blog/2013/07/02/setup-redis</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Redis 的安装超级简单，可以说对于任何级别的 Linux 用户都没有障碍。</p>

<p>只需简单几步即可搞定：</p>

<ul>
<li>下载源码。</li>
</ul>


<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>wget http://redis.googlecode.com/files/redis-2.6.14.tar.gz</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<ul>
<li>解压编译。</li>
</ul>


<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>$ tar vzxf redis-2.6.14.tar.gz
</span><span class='line'>$ cd redis-2.6.14
</span><span class='line'>$ make</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<ul>
<li>然后直接启动编译好的二进制 server 端：</li>
</ul>


<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>$ src/redis-server</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<ul>
<li>这时打开客户端即可尝试一下 Redis 的语法了：</li>
</ul>


<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>$ src/redis-cli
</span><span class='line'>redis&gt; set foo bar
</span><span class='line'>OK
</span><span class='line'>redis&gt; get foo
</span><span class='line'>"bar"</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>原文：<a href="http://redis.io/download">http://redis.io/download</a></p>
